# Ecommerce Revenue & Product Performance Dashboard

## Project Overview

This Power BI dashboard analyzes 16,650 ecommerce transactions to evaluate revenue performance, customer activity, product performance, and return behavior.

### Business Question

How is revenue performing, and which products are driving sales and returns?

## Tools Used

* Power BI Desktop
* DAX
* SQL

## Dashboard Preview

![Dashboard Overview](dashboard-overview.png)


## Key Metrics

* Total Sales: 336,629.89
* Total Refunds: -59,110.01
* Net Revenue: 277,519.88
* Return Rate: 17.56%
* Total Customers: 453

## Key Insights

* Top 10 customers contributed 25.98% of total revenue.
* Friday generated the highest revenue activity.
* January recorded the highest net revenue among all months analyzed.
* Several of the most returned products were Christmas-themed items, suggesting seasonal products experienced higher return volumes.
* Returns accounted for 17.56% of total sales revenue.

## Dashboard Components

### KPI Cards

* Total Sales
* Total Refunds
* Net Revenue
* Return Rate
* Total Customers

### Revenue Analysis

* Monthly Net Revenue Trend
* Net Revenue by Day of Week

### Product Analysis

* Top 10 Revenue-Generating Products
* Top 10 Most Returned Products

